      "content": "Complete guide to installing AkiraDocs in different environments."
    },
    {
      "id": "2",
      "type": "heading",
      "content": "Prerequisites",
      "metadata": {
        "level": 2
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "3",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "Ensure your system meets the [requirements](../getting-started/requirements.md) before proceeding."
    },
    {
      "id": "4",
      "type": "heading",
      "content": "Installation Methods",
      "metadata": {
        "level": 2
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "5",
      "type": "heading",
      "content": "1. Local Development Setup",
      "metadata": {
        "level": 3
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "6",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "1. <strong>Create New Project</strong>"
    },
    {
      "id": "7",
      "type": "code",
      "content": "npx create-akiradocs@latest my-docs-site\ncd my-docs-site",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "bash",
        "showLineNumbers": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "8",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "2. <strong>Install Dependencies</strong>\nDependencies are automatically installed during project creation. If you need to reinstall:"
    },
    {
      "id": "9",
      "type": "code",
      "content": "npm install",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "bash",
        "showLineNumbers": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "10",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "3. <strong>Create Environment File</strong>\nThe environment file is created automatically. You can modify it at `.env.local`"
    },
    {
      "id": "11",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "4. <strong>Start Development Server</strong>"
    },
    {
      "id": "12",
      "type": "code",
      "content": "npm run dev",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "bash",
        "showLineNumbers": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "13",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "5. <strong>Update AkiraDocs</strong>\nTo update an existing installation to the latest version:"
    },
    {
      "id": "14",
      "type": "code",
      "content": "npx create-akiradocs@latest update",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "bash",
        "showLineNumbers": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "15",
      "type": "heading",
      "content": "3. Cloud Platform Deployment",
      "metadata": {
        "level": 3
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "16",
      "type": "heading",
      "content": "Vercel",
      "metadata": {
        "level": 4
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "17",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "1. Fork the repository\n2. Connect to Vercel\n3. Configure environment variables\n4. Deploy"
    },
    {
      "id": "18",
      "type": "heading",
      "content": "Other Platforms",
      "metadata": {
